      "date": "2011-08-10 02:51:45.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 2: Verified\n\nTests received by maloo, run on rhel/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/c4b64dc4-c2fa-11e0-9a20-52540025f9af).  Ran 12 tests.  No failures.",
